    So, theres really NO reason NOT to reg. this door... i understand if
   you are not living in denmark, the phonecosts ect. so therefor there's
   NO LIMITATIONS in the unregistered version, the ONLY difference between
       it and a regged one, is your name in it! - and you saying that
